{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/actionprotocol\/getstatehint()"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getStateHint"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is returned it either means that the action is not stateful","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or that there is no hint about the valid range of values for the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state of the action."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a [type[Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant] array is returned then each item in the array is a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"possible value for the state.  If a [type[Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant] pair (ie: two-tuple) is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"returned then the tuple specifies the inclusive lower and upper bound","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of valid values for the state.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In any case, the information is merely a hint.  It may be possible to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"have a state value outside of the hinted range and setting a value","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within the range may fail."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The return value (if non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"type":"text","text":") should be freed with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Variant.unref"},{"text":"] when it is no longer required.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getStateHint()"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"getStateHint()","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getStateHint","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"VariantRef"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:3GIO14ActionProtocolPAAE12getStateHint4GLib10VariantRefVSgyF","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","symbolKind":"method"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Requests a hint about the valid range of values for the state of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"action","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol"]]},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ActionProtocol/getStateHint()":{"title":"getStateHint()","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getStateHint()","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/actionprotocol\/getstatehint()","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"getStateHint","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Requests a hint about the valid range of values for the state of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"action"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ActionProtocol":{"role":"symbol","title":"ActionProtocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ActionProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ActionProtocol"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/actionprotocol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GAction"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a single named action."}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"}}}